item.title: RAAR - label
item.description: Two of techno’s brightest shards, the oft-collaborating Maelstrom and LOUISAHHH!!! are delighted to present the label RAAR. The name connotes both ‘rare, uncommon, unique’ and the sound of a guttural roar, the wild cry of a true passion project. Started as equal parts research division of techno’s new frontiers, haven for the sacred and profane, and ‘benevolent anarchy’, RAAR aims to release truly innovative music from and for brave sonic explorers.
